ith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/19\/takfir-wrongful-accusation-backfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":7652,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Takfir: False charges of unbelief backfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a man calls his brother an unbeliever, it turns against at least one of them.\u00a0Either the accused is as he claimed, or else the charge will turn against him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6104, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33548,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/18\/o-allah-make-faith-beloved\/","url_meta":{"origin":7652,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: O Allah, make faith in Islam beloved in our hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah ibn Rafi\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, make faith beloved to us and beautify it in our hearts, and make unbelief, wickedness, and disobedience hateful to us, and make us among the rightly-guided. O Allah, let us pass away as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0